<i>noun</i>: 중용 [중용], 절제 [절쩨] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>중용 [중용]</dt><br>
<dd>moderation</dd><br>
<dd>넘치거나 모자라지 않고 어느 한쪽으로 치우치지 않은 상태나 정도.</dd><br>
<dd>A state or degree that is neither excessive nor insufficient and not biased to either side.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>절제 [절쩨]</dt><br>
<dd>restraint; moderation</dd><br>
<dd>정도에 넘지 않도록 알맞게 조절하여 제한함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of regulating and limiting something so it will not exceed a certain degree.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>